    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-cardiovascular-modeling-group-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. The CFD hemolysis model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The assessment supports pre-market submission to FDA. Decision: Accepted.",
